cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with privacy-preserving systems for data ownership using blockchain and distributed databases. The primary focus is on cryptography and security (cs.CR) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for data processing (cs.LG), the ethical and legal implications of data privacy (cs.CY), and information retrieval techniques for searching encrypted data (cs.IR).
